      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via an M Variable Differential Lock. Technical highlights include recent VANOS servicing and rod bearing replacement, addressing key longevity concerns for this platform. The chassis remains composed thanks to a refreshed suspension setup with Bilstein dampers and reinforced rear subframe mounting points. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-enjoyed enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical synchronization and throttle mapping remain exceptionally sharp, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
